1931;;Border Law;;American;;Louis King;;Buck Jones, Jim Mason, Lupita Tovar;;western;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Border_Law;;Captain Wilks (F.R. Smith) of the Texas Rangers orders Jim Houston (Buck Jones) and his crew, Thunder Rogers (Frank Rice) and Jim's brother Bob (Don Chapman), to go to Eureka, Texas to break up the Shag Smith (Jim Mason) gang.[2]